Introducing, @sabrinacarpenter’s secret to the best beauty sleep, our 🆕 Acidic Bonding Concentrate 24/7 Night and Day Serum 🖤​

​As the 1st bonding serum for 24/7 repair, this serum provides. . .​

✨ The power of citric acid to penetrate 7 layers deep and strengthen strands* ​
✨ 3x more hydrated hair**​
✨ 89% less breakage ​
✨Overnight protection ​
✨72% less frizz after 8 hours vs. untreated hair*​

​In other words, this serum works late so you don’t have to 🤝  Ready to meet repair that never sleeps? ​

​*continued use of system of abc shampoo, conditioner, and serum vs. untreated hair ​
**system of abc shampoo, conditioner, and serum vs. non-conditioning shampoo ​
